# HTTP2/GRPC based Patterns

## Why http2 over http 1.1

1. ### Web Performance ### : A detailed control available to developers over prioritization. Which peiece of content to load first is controlled via **weighted prioritization**.
via multiplexing server sends the content over multiple data streams, each stream has different weighted value, value tells the client which one to render first. 
This works great for content serving - need to see whether there would be any benifits for application/services. Same strict origin issues causes 

